{"tid":2326861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［是日笑話］監警會主席梁定邦：不知是否市民失信心","createTime":"2020-12-15T15:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T15:42:26.000Z","uid":176279,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1e677240e0c9957e560e29fdc3e4e676ef9710","tid":2326861,"uid":176279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416733&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGFUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=8ea795ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416733&h=6b643f9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416733</a><br />\n<br />\n監警會主席梁定邦：「市民對監警會是否無信心？在這個階段我不知道，因為要做一些更積極研究。其實很多人對我說對我們很有信心，但這是否可代表全體市民？我不知道。所以我相信在這個階段，大家可得到此結論市民對監警會沒有信心。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">「失」意思（國語辭典修訂版）<br />\n[動]<br />\n<br />\n1.丟掉、遺落。如：「喪失」、「遺失」、「失而復得」、「失魂落魄」。<br />\n2.錯過、縱放。如：「錯失良機」、「機不可失」。<br />\n3.找不到。如：「迷失方向」。《楚辭．屈原．九章．惜誦》：「欲橫奔而失路兮，堅志而不忍。」<br />\n4.違背、不合乎。如：「失常」、「失態」、「失禮」。<br />\n<br />\n[名]<br />\n錯誤。如：「過失」、「智者千慮必有一失。」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n正確「失」字用法：<br />\n監警會既存在就係一個「失」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「有」過先可以「失」</span>"},{"pid":"44ed058bfdbe1b149b417c19272ec6a934ea1beb","tid":2326861,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bfb021abad5d81900deebaa34a8be131884338b","tid":2326861,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"梁x邦：<br />\n你及你個會是廢柴<br />\n完"},{"pid":"13180cd564414bd2c0b964679806de7093a6c838","tid":2326861,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"同伍熟ching一樣？<br />\n失去啲本身就冇嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi